No Red Roses by Iris Johansen

Genre: Romance

Date: 2013-10-29 Format: pdf,epub,mobi	Language: English 
Pages: 320

This is another sweet story from Iris Johansen. In addition to Rex and Tamara, Jenny and Steve from 'Return to Santa Flores" makes an appearance in this story as well. This time Tamara as well as Jenny get themselves into a scrape that Rex has to get them out of. This is a nice, sweet heartfelt story whose emotions will touch you and make you smile.
